JOHANNESBURG - A daughter of one of the congregants of the Mancoba Seven Angels Ministry in eNgcobo, says her mother gave her entire pension to the church. Her mother and younger siblings were among the people who have been removed from the church after a police raid at the weekend. Police raided the church on Friday night and shot dead seven men suspected of having attacked the Ngcobo police station earlier in the week. Watch the video above for the full interview. eNCA